  "description": {
    "de": "Dieses Schwert wurde dem jungen Iop Blackcat zu seinem Ritterschlag verliehen. Leider stürzte dieser gleich bei seiner ersten Mission als Ritter und zerschmetterte sein Schwert. Er hatte nämlich einen Krachler für einen harmlosen Stein gehalten.",
    "en": "The legends tell of a famous Iop who left his island home and travelled across the sea to find work as an interpreter for the Kings of Amakna. He took to the job full of hope, enthusiasm and diligence, dazzling Ecaflips and Fecas alike with his vibrant wordplay and passion for good grammar. Unfortunately, on his way to the castle, he stumbled over a rock that turned out to be a Mega Crackler, and this broken sword was the only trace they found of him, or his equipment.",
    "es": "Esta espada ha sido un regalo para la armadura de gala de un joven yopuka llamado Bajo Skalera. Desafortunadamente, durante su primera misión como caballero, resbaló sobre una piedra. En realidad, aquella piedra era el dedo meñique del pie de un crujidor...",
    "fr": "Cette épée fut donnée à Souzé Schel, un jeune Iop, lors de son adoubement. Malheureusement, lors de sa première mission de chevalier, il glissa sur une pierre qui se trouvait être un craqueleur...",
    "id": "44960",
    "pt": "Um jovem seguidor de lop, Souze Schel, recebeu essa espada para seu treino. Infelizmente, durante sua primeira missão, ele tropeçou em uma pedra que, na verdade, era um Smagador..."
  },
